    "In total the dataset contains 490 classes (488 for treatments and 2 for negative controls), 8,423,455 individual single-cells (47% treatment and 53% control cells).",
    "See Venn diagrams in Fig. 4 for more details.",
    "This study uses machine learning to analyze publicly available Cell Painting datasets with the goal of understanding image-based profiling methodologies.",
    "No statistical method was used to predetermine sample size.",
    "Certain images were excluded from the analysis following the quality control procedure described in the \"Benchmarks and ground truth annotations\" section of the Methods."
